# Google Sheets API Configuration
# Choose ONE of the following methods:

# Method 1: Service Account Key File (recommended for local development)
# Download the JSON key file from Google Cloud Console and set the path:
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY_FILE=./path/to/service-account-key.json

# Method 2: Service Account Key as Environment Variable (recommended for production)
# Copy the entire JSON content as a string:
# GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY='{"type":"service_account","project_id":"your-project",...}'

